5. Keep commits focused on single features

## Architecture

### Frontend (Preact)

State Management:
- Global state managed with Zustand
- Clip data, timeline state, playback controls
- Workspace persistence through Tauri IPC

Component Hierarchy:
```
App
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Header (Import, Export, Controls)
